quran[8{c,v,t}:
6,45,is terhan un logon ki jarr kaat kar rakh di gayi jinhon ne zulm kya tha aur tareef hai Allah rab alaalmin ke liye ( ke is ne un ki jarr kaat di )
6,46,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho, kabhi tum ne yeh bhi socha ke agar Allah tumhari benaye aur samaat tum se chean le aur tumahray dilon par mohar kar day to Allah ke siwa aur kon sa khuda hai jo yeh quwaten tumhe wapas dlaskta ho? dekho, kis terhan hum baar baar apni nishanain un ke samnay paish karte hain aur phir yeh kis terhan un se nazar chura jatay hain"
6,47,"kaho, kabhi tum ne socha ke agar Allah ki taraf se achanak ya alania tum par azaab aa jaye to kya zalim logon ke siwa koi aur halaak hoga ?"
6,48,hum jo rasool bhaijtay hain isi liye to bhaijtay hain ke woh naik kirdaar logon ke liye khush khaberi dainay walay aur bad krdaron ke liye darane walay hon phir jo log un ki baat maan len aur apne tarz amal ki islaah kar len un ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai
6,49,aur jo hamari ayaat kojjhutlainwoh apni nafarmanio-n ki Padaash mein saza bhagat kar rahen ge
6,50,"a y Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho,"" mein tum se yeh nahi kehta ke mere paas Allah ke khazanay hain nah mein ghaib ka ilm rakhta hon, aur nah yeh kehta hon ke mein farishta hon mein to sirf uss wahi ki pairwi karta hon jo mujh par nazil ki jati hai"" phir un se pucho kya andha aur aankhon wala dono barabar ho saktay hain? kya tum ghhor nahi karte ?"
6,51,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tum is ( ilm wahi ) ke zareya se unn logon ko nasiyaat karo jo is baat ka khauf rakhtay hain ke apne rab ke samnay kabhi is haal mein paish kiye jayen ge ke uss ke siwa wahan koi ( aisa Zee Iqtidaar ) nah hoga jo un ka haami o madad gaar ho, ya un ki sifarish kere, shayad ke ( is nasiyaat se mutnabba ho kar ) woh khuda tarsi ki rawish ikhtiyar kar len"
6,52,aur jo log apne rab ko raat din pkarte rehtay hain o ray is ki khushnodi ki talab mein lagey hue hain inhen apne se daur nah phenko unn ke hisaab mein se kisi cheez ka baar tum par nahi hai aur tumahray hisaab mein se kisi cheez ka baar unn par nahi is par bhi agar tum inhen daur phenko ge to zaalmon mein shumaar ho ge
